decl: example (i : I) (injf : Injective f) : (⋂ i, f '' A i) ⊆ f '' ⋂ i, A i
og_raw:
example (i : I) (injf : Injective f) : (⋂ i, f '' A i) ⊆ f '' ⋂ i, A i := by
  intro y; simp
  intro h
  rcases h i with ⟨x, xAi, fxeq⟩
  use x; constructor
  · intro i'
    rcases h i' with ⟨x', x'Ai, fx'eq⟩
    have : f x = f x' := by rw [fxeq, fx'eq]
    have : x = x' := injf this
    rw [this]
    exact x'Ai
  exact fxeq
new_raw:
example (i : I) (injf : Injective f) : (⋂ i, f '' A i) ⊆ f '' ⋂ i, A i   := by
  rintro y h; rcases h i with ⟨x, xAi, rfl⟩
  exact ⟨x, fun i' => let ⟨x', x'Ai, hx'⟩ := h i' in injf hx'.symm ▸ x'Ai, rfl⟩

decl: example : (f ⁻¹' ⋃ i, B i) = ⋃ i, f ⁻¹' B i
og_raw:
example : (f ⁻¹' ⋃ i, B i) = ⋃ i, f ⁻¹' B i := by
  ext x
  simp
new_raw:
example : (f ⁻¹' ⋃ i, B i) = ⋃ i, f ⁻¹' B i  := by
  simp

decl: example : (f ⁻¹' ⋂ i, B i) = ⋂ i, f ⁻¹' B i
og_raw:
example : (f ⁻¹' ⋂ i, B i) = ⋂ i, f ⁻¹' B i := by
  ext x
  simp
new_raw:
example : (f ⁻¹' ⋂ i, B i) = ⋂ i, f ⁻¹' B i  := by
  simp [preimage_iInter]

og_raw:
example : InjOn sqrt { x | x ≥ 0 } := by
  intro x xnonneg y ynonneg
  intro e
  calc
    x = sqrt x ^ 2 := by rw [sq_sqrt xnonneg]
    _ = sqrt y ^ 2 := by rw [e]
    _ = y := by rw [sq_sqrt ynonneg]
new_raw:
example : InjOn sqrt { x | x ≥ 0 }  := by
  rintro x (hx : 0 ≤ x) y (hy : 0 ≤ y) h
  rw [← sq_sqrt hx, ← sq_sqrt hy, h]

decl: example : InjOn (fun x ↦ x ^ 2) { x : ℝ | x ≥ 0 }
og_raw:
example : InjOn (fun x ↦ x ^ 2) { x : ℝ | x ≥ 0 } := by
  intro x xnonneg y ynonneg
  intro e
  dsimp at *
  calc
    x = sqrt (x ^ 2) := by rw [sqrt_sq xnonneg]
    _ = sqrt (y ^ 2) := by rw [e]
    _ = y := by rw [sqrt_sq ynonneg]
new_raw:
example : InjOn (fun x ↦ x ^ 2) { x : ℝ | x ≥ 0 }  := by
  rintro x (hx : 0 ≤ x) y (hy : 0 ≤ y) (h : x ^ 2 = y ^ 2)
  rw [←sqrt_sq hx, h, sqrt_sq hy]

decl: example : sqrt '' { x | x ≥ 0 } = { y | y ≥ 0 }
og_raw:
example : sqrt '' { x | x ≥ 0 } = { y | y ≥ 0 } := by
  ext y; constructor
  · rintro ⟨x, ⟨xnonneg, rfl⟩⟩
    apply sqrt_nonneg
  intro ynonneg
  use y ^ 2
  dsimp at *
  constructor
  apply pow_nonneg ynonneg
  apply sqrt_sq
  assumption
new_raw:
example : sqrt '' { x | x ≥ 0 } = { y | y ≥ 0 }   := by
  ext y; constructor
  · rintro ⟨x, -, rfl⟩
    exact sqrt_nonneg _
  · rintro (ynonneg: y ≥ 0)
    exact ⟨y^2, pow_nonneg ynonneg _, sqrt_sq ynonneg⟩

decl: example : (range fun x ↦ x ^ 2) = { y : ℝ | y ≥ 0 }
og_raw:
example : (range fun x ↦ x ^ 2) = { y : ℝ | y ≥ 0 } := by
  ext y
  constructor
  · rintro ⟨x, rfl⟩
    dsimp at *
    apply pow_two_nonneg
  intro ynonneg
  use sqrt y
  exact sq_sqrt ynonneg
new_raw:
example : (range fun x ↦ x ^ 2) = { y : ℝ | y ≥ 0 }  := by
  ext y
  constructor
  rintro ⟨x, rfl⟩
  exact pow_two_nonneg x
  intro ynonneg
  use sqrt y
  exact sq_sqrt ynonneg

decl: theorem inverse_spec {f : α → β} (y : β) (h : ∃ x, f x = y) : f (inverse f y) = y
og_raw:
theorem inverse_spec {f : α → β} (y : β) (h : ∃ x, f x = y) : f (inverse f y) = y := by
  rw [inverse, dif_pos h]
  exact Classical.choose_spec h
new_raw:
theorem inverse_spec {f : α → β} (y : β) (h : ∃ x, f x = y) : f (inverse f y) = y  := by
  rw [inverse, dif_pos h, Classical.choose_spec h]
